{"type": "article", "id": 19798, "title": "“吐司”沙发", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-28T07:40:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104209cuEKt7p2RahBT04O.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这块巨型“吐司”是一张单人沙发，也可以平放在地面上做为一张垫子。沙发的弧形外轮廓是棕色的，正反都是白色的绒毛，令人联想到吐司的松软和诱人，显得活泼可爱。甚至可以把它看做半个绒毛玩具，是一个不错的送礼选择。<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/dp/B00AH7XG70/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=674sm-20&amp;linkId=d37c2137165b87ecb3f18f1543d59e05\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150211t8gsmifKrGIaSPXq.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"447\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.894\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150211mn8dBfQNZKgxSA5l.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150212NxD8c1gUTqLwQaCP.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261502132Kik5MWEzahwO4vJ.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}